#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Pitanja i odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This chapter addresses a number of issues that frequently cause "
#| "confusion, especially in new users of &kappname;. If you find that "
#| "&kappname; is doing something you don't understand (or sometimes not "
#| "doing something you want it to do,) please check this list before asking "
#| "for help on one of the mailing lists. If your problem is not mentioned "
#| "here, refer to the section on <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">getting "
#| "help</link>."
msgid ""
"This chapter addresses a number of issues that frequently cause confusion, "
"especially for new users of &kmymoney;. If you find that &kmymoney; is doing "
"something you don't understand (or sometimes not doing something you want it "
"to do,) please check this list before asking for help on one of the mailing "
"lists. If your problem is not mentioned here, refer to the section on <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">getting help</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ovo poglavlje se bavi brojnim problemima koji često izazivaju konfuziju, "
"posebno kod novih korisnka &kappname;. Ukoliko &kappname; radi nešto što ne "
"razumijete (ili nekada radi nešto što ne želite), molimo provjerite ovu "
"listu prije traženja pomoći na jednoj od mail listi. Ako vaš problem nije "
"spomenut ovdje, posjetite dio na <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">getting "
"help</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation and Startup Questions"
msgstr "Pitanja vezana za instalaciju i pokretanje"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; crashes when I try to launch it."
msgid "&kmymoney; crashes when I try to launch it."
msgstr "&kappname; se krahira kada ga pokušam pokrenuti."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many reasons &kmymoney; might crash or give an error instead of "
"starting up normally. Sometimes an error message is shown, but if not, you "
"can run &kmymoney; from a command line, to see if any useful information is "
"output to the console. On &Linux;, this just means typing \"kmymoney\" in a "
"shell. &macOS; should be similar. On &Windows;, you will need to type the "
"full path to the &kmymoney; executable."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:38
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are many reasons &kappname; might crash or give an error instead of "
#| "starting up normally. You first need to determine if the problem is with "
#| "the software or with your data. So, the first thing to try is to <link "
#| "linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">launch &kappname;</link> without opening "
#| "your data file. If the application starts up, but crashes when you try to "
#| "load your data file, try loading an older copy of your file. (You did "
#| "make a backup, didn't you?)"
msgid ""
"If this does not show the cause of the problem, you need to determine if "
"there is an issue with the software or with your data. To do this, you need "
"to <link linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">launch &kmymoney;</link> without "
"opening your data file. If the application starts up, but crashes when you "
"try to load your data file, try loading an older copy of your file. (You did "
"make a backup, didn't you?)"
msgstr ""
"Postoji mnogi razlozi zbog kojih &kappname; može krahirati ili prijaviti "
"grešku umjesto normalnog pokretanja. Prvo trebate ustanoviti ako je problem "
"u softveru ili u vašim podacima. Dakle, prva stvar koju trebate pokušati je "
"<link linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">pokreni &kappname;</link> bez otvaranja "
"vaše datoteke sa podacima. Ako se aplikacija pokrene, ali krahira kad "
"pokušate učitati vašu datoteku sa podacima, pokušajte učitati stariju kopiju "
"vaše datoteke. (Napravili ste rezervu, zar ne?)"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:46
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If &kappname; crashes on startup without trying to load a data file, "
#| "there may be a problem with your installation. See the section on <link "
#| "linkend=\"installation\">installing &kappname;</link> or the section on "
#| "<link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">getting help</link>."
msgid ""
"If &kmymoney; crashes on startup without trying to load a data file, there "
"may be a problem with your installation. See the section on <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.contact\">getting help</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ako se &kappname; krahira prilikom pokretanja bez pokušaja učitavanja "
"datoteke sa podacima, možda je problen u vašoj instalaciji. Pogledajte dio "
"na <link linkend=\"installation\">instaliranje &kappname;</link> ili dio na "
"<link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">pomoć</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Will &kappname; work on my X/&ubuntu; desktop? Will &kappname; work "
#| "without a full KDE desktop?"
msgid ""
"Will &kmymoney; work on my X/&ubuntu; desktop? Will &kmymoney; work without "
"a full &kde; desktop?"
msgstr ""
"Hoće li &kappname; raditi na mom X/&ubuntu; desktop računaru? Hoće li "
"&kappname; raditi bez punog KDE desktop računara."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes, &kappname; will work without a full &kde; desktop, but you will have "
#| "to install the basic &kde; libraries first. The easiest way to do this is "
#| "to use <link linkend=\"installation.distribution\">your distribution's "
#| "package management system</link>, which will handle these requirements "
#| "automatically. If you are going to install from source, you will probably "
#| "need development versions of those libraries; refer to these <link "
#| "linkend=\"installation.fromsource\">instructions</link> for details."
msgid ""
"Yes, &kmymoney; will work without a full &kde; desktop, but you will have to "
"install the basic &kde; libraries first. The easiest way to do this is to "
"use your distribution's package management system, which will handle these "
"requirements automatically. If you are going to install from source, you "
"will probably need development versions of those libraries."
msgstr ""
"Da, &kappname; će raditi bez punog &kde; desktop računara, ali ćete prvo "
"morati instalirati bazne &kde; biblioteke. Najlakši način da uradite ovo je "
"da koristite <link linkend=\"installation.distribution\"> sistem paketnog "
"menadžmenta vašeg izdanja</link>, koji će obrađivati ove zahtjeve "
"automatski. Ako ćete instalirati iz izvora, vjerovatno ćete trebati razvojne "
"verzije ovih biblioteka; pogledajte ove <link linkend=\"installation."
"fromsource\">upute</link> za detaljne informacije."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration Questions"
msgstr "Pitanja o konfiguraciji"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can I change the start of the fiscal year, to match my tax year or "
"accounting year?"
msgstr ""
"Mogu li promijeniti početak fiskalne godine, tako da se slaže sa mojom "
"poreznom ili računovodstvenom godinom?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes, you can easily set the start of the year in the <link linkend="
#| "\"details.settings.general.global\">Global Options</link> section of the "
#| "<guilabel>Configure &kappname;</guilabel> dialog."
msgid ""
"Yes, you can easily set the start of the year in the <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.general.global\">Global Options</link> section of the "
"<guilabel>Configure &kmymoney;</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Da, lako možete podesiti početak godine u <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"general.global\">Globalne Opcije</link> paragrafu <guilabel>Konfiguriši "
"&kappname;</guilabel> dijaloga."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account and Transaction Questions"
msgstr "Pitanja u vezi računa i transakcija"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I edit a transaction?"
msgstr "Zašto ne mogu urediti transakciju?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:97
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You cannot make any changes to a transaction with a date before the "
#| "opening date of the account it is in. The most common reason for this is "
#| "importing all the data for an account. If the import file does not "
#| "contain an opening date for the account, &kappname; will use the current "
#| "date. The way to fix this is to edit the account, and <link linkend="
#| "\"details.accounts.edit\">change the opening date</link> to be earlier "
#| "than any transaction in that account."
msgid ""
"You cannot make any changes to a transaction with a date before the opening "
"date of the account it is in. The most common reason for this is importing "
"all the data for an account. If the import file does not contain an opening "
"date for the account, &kmymoney; will use the current date. The way to fix "
"this is to edit the account, and <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit"
"\">change the opening date</link> to be earlier than any transaction in that "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Ne možete napraviti bilo kakve promjene na transakciji sa datumom ranijim od "
"datuma otvaranja računa u kojem se nalazi. Najčešći razlog za ovo je uvoz "
"svih podataka za račun. Ako datoteka sa koje su uvozi ne sadrži datum "
"otvaranja računa, &kappname; će koristiti tekući datum. Način da popravite "
"ovo je da uredite račun, i <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">promijeni "
"datum otvaranja</link> tako da taj datum bude raniji od svih transakcija u "
"tom računu."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why is a transaction shown in red and how can I get rid of the color?"
msgstr "Zašto je transakcija prikazana u crvenom i kako se mogu riješiti boje?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A transaction is shown in red if any part of the amount has not been "
"assigned to a category. This is most commonly caused by importing a QIF or "
"OFX file or by downloading statement data online. All you have to do is to "
"modify the transaction such that the whole amount of the transaction is "
"assigned to categories."
msgstr ""
"Transakcija je prikazana u crvenom ako bilo koji dio iznosa nije dodijeljen "
"kategoriji. Ovo je najčešće uzrokavano uvozom QIF ili OFX datoteka ili "
"preuzimanjem podataka izvoda iz računa sa interneta. Sve što trebate uraditi "
"jeste modificirati transakciju tako da je cijeli iznos transakcije "
"dodijeljen kategorijama."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I add an opening balance to an account?"
msgstr "Zašto ne mogu dodati početno stanje na račun?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you provide an opening balance when you create an account, it is shown as "
"the first transaction for the account. If you do not, then the transaction "
"is not there, and because it is a special type of transaction, you cannot "
"simply add it as you could a deposit or withdrawal. However, you can add it "
"later by <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">editing the account</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ako postavite početno stanje prilikom kreiranja računa, to je prikazano u "
"obliku prve transakcije za taj račun. Ako to ne uradite, onda transakcija "
"neće biti tu, i zato što je ovo posebna vrsta transakcije, ne možete je "
"jednostavno dodati kao što biste dodali depozit ili podizanje novca sa "
"računa. Međutim, možete je dodati kasnije preko <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.edit\">uređivanje računa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I created an account, I used the wrong type, and now it won't let me "
"change it. I can edit the account, but the dropdown for account type is "
"either disabled, or does not list all the possible types."
msgstr ""
"Kada sam kreirao/la račun, koristio sam pogrešan tip, i sada mi ne "
"dozvoljava promjenu. Mogu urediti račun, ali padajući meni za ovaj tip "
"računa je ili isključen, ili ne izlistava sve moguće tipove."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:149
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can easily change an account type between checking, savings, and "
#| "cash. However, because of the way &kappname; stores the account "
#| "information, it does not allow other changes of account type. The way "
#| "around this is to create a new account of the correct type, move all the "
#| "transactions from the old to the new account, and then delete the old "
#| "account."
msgid ""
"You can easily change an account type between checking, savings, and cash. "
"However, because of the way &kmymoney; stores the account information, it "
"does not allow other changes of account type. The way around this is to "
"<link linkend=\"details.accounts.create\">create a new account of the "
"correct type</link>, move all the transactions from the old to the new "
"account, and then <link linkend=\"details.accounts.delete\"> delete the old "
"account.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Možete lako promijeniti tip računa u čekovni, štedni, i keš. Međutim, zbog "
"načina na koji &kappname; pohranjuje informacije o računima, ne dozvoljava "
"ostale promjene računa. Način da zaobiđete ovo je da kreirate novi račun "
"ispravnog tipa, prenesete sve transakcije iz starog u novi račun, i onda "
"obrišete stari račun."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:164
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "I have a loan with 0% interest, but I get an error in the new loan wizard "
#| "that does not let me use this value."
msgid ""
"I have a loan with 0% interest, but I get an error in the New Loan Wizard "
"that does not let me use this value."
msgstr ""
"Imam kredit sa 0% kamate, ali dobijem grešku u kontroli za novi kredit koja "
"mi ne dozvoljava da koristim ovu vrijednost,."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The internal calculations of the new loan wizard do not allow a 0% interest "
"rate. The best way to handle this situation is to <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.create.account\">create a simple liability account</link> with a "
"starting balance for the amount of the loan, and then <link linkend="
"\"details.schedules.new\">create a schedule</link> for the required payments."
msgstr ""
"Interna izračunavanja kontrole za novi kredit ne dozvoljavaju 0% kamate. "
"Najbolji način da se nosite sa ovom situacijom je <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.create.account\">kreiraj jednostavan račun za dugovanja</link> sa "
"početnim stanjem iznosa kredita, i onda <link linkend=\"details.schedules.new"
"\">kreiraj novi raspored</link>  za tražene uplate."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why don't I see all my transactions in the ledger?"
msgstr "Zašto ne vidim sve svoje transakcije u knjizi salda?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:185
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are several settings that control which transactions are displayed "
#| "in the ledger view of an account. First, check the <link linkend="
#| "\"details.ledgers.view.filter\">ledger filter area</link>. If there is "
#| "anything typed in the search box, only transactions containing that text "
#| "will be shown. If the status dropdown has been changed from <quote>Any "
#| "status,</quote> then only transaction of the selected type will be shown. "
#| "In addition, there are two important settings in the <link linkend="
#| "\"details.settings.general.filter\">filter options</link> section on the "
#| "&kappname; Settings dialog. If the <guilabel>Do not show transactions "
#| "prior to</guilabel> field is set, only transactions on or after that date "
#| "will be shown in the ledger. If the <guilabel>Do not show reconciled "
#| "transactions</guilabel> box is checked, then no reconciled transactions "
#| "will be shown."
msgid ""
"There are several settings that control which transactions are displayed in "
"the Ledger View of an account. First, check the <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.view.filter\">ledger filter area</link>. If there is anything typed "
"in the search box, only transactions containing that text will be shown. If "
"the status dropdown has been changed from <quote>Any status,</quote> then "
"only transaction of the selected type will be shown. In addition, there are "
"two important settings in the <link linkend=\"details.settings.general.filter"
"\">filter options</link> section on the &kmymoney; Settings dialog. If the "
"<guilabel>Do not show transactions prior to</guilabel> field is set, only "
"transactions on or after that date will be shown in the ledger. If the "
"<guilabel>Do not show reconciled transactions</guilabel> box is checked, "
"then no reconciled transactions will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Postoji nekoliko opcija koje kontrolišu koje će transakcije biti prikazane u "
"knjizi salda nekog računa. Prvo, provjerite <link linkend=\"details.ledgers."
"view.filter\">oblast filtera knjige salda</link>. Ako je išta uneseno u "
"okviru za pretragu, samo transakcije koje sadrže taj tekts će biti "
"prikazane. Ako je opadajuci okvir statusa promijenjen iz <quote>Bilo koji "
"status,</quote> tada će samo transakcije odabranog tipa biti prikazane. "
"Dodatno, tu su i dvije važne postavke u <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"general.filter\">opcije filtera</link> u &kappname; dijalgou postavki. Ako "
"je polje <guilabel>Ne prikazuj transakcije prije</guilabel> uključeno, samo "
"transakcije sa kasnijim datumom će biti prikazane u knjizi salda. Ako je "
"okvir <guilabel>Ne prikazuj usklađene transakcije</guilabel> zakačen, tada "
"neće biti prikazana nijedna usklađena transakcija."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I mistyped the name of a payee and want to change it in all transaction. Is "
"there a global search/replace?"
msgstr ""
"Pogrešno sam unio/la ime primatelja uplate i želim da ga promijenim u svim "
"transakcijama. Postoji li opcija globalnog pretraživanja/zamjene?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There is no global search and replace function in KMyMoney. Nevertheless, "
#| "it is easy to change a payees name: select the Payees view and find the "
#| "entry with the name you want to change. Click with the &RMB; on the "
#| "payee, and select <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Rename payee</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>. Enter the new name. Since the transactions only use a "
#| "reference to the payees record, all transactions now show the new name."
msgid ""
"There is no global search and replace function in &kmymoney;. Nevertheless, "
"it is easy to change a payee's name: select the Payees View and find the "
"entry with the name you want to change. Click with the &RMB; on the payee, "
"select <guimenuitem>Rename payee</guimenuitem> from the context menu, and "
"enter the new name. Since the transactions only use a reference to the "
"payees record, all transactions now show the new name."
msgstr ""
"Ne postoji funkcija za globalno pretraživanje i zamjenu u KMyMoney. Unatoč "
"tome, lako je promjeniti ime primatelja uplate: odaberite pregled primatelja "
"uplata i nađite unos sa imenom koje želite promijeniti. Kliknite sa &RMB; "
"(desnom tipkom miša) na primatelja uplate, i odaberite  "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Promijenite ime primatelja uplate</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Unesite novo ime. Kako transakcije koriste samo referencu na "
"dosije primatelja uplata, sada sve transakcije prikazuju novo ime."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I delete an account?"
msgstr "Zašto ne mogu obrisati račun?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:227
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In order to delete an account, &kappname; can have no other references to "
#| "it. That means you must delete all transactions, or move them to another "
#| "account. If you still can't delete an account, there may be scheduled "
#| "transactions referring to that account, which may not be visible in the "
#| "ledger. You need to delete any future transactions and the schedule "
#| "itself, or switch them to a different account."
msgid ""
"In order to delete an account, &kmymoney; can have no other references to "
"it. That means you must delete all transactions from that account or move "
"them to another account. If you still can't delete an account, there may be "
"scheduled transactions referring to that account, which may not be visible "
"in the ledger. You need to delete any future transactions and the schedule "
"itself, or switch them to a different account."
msgstr ""
"Da bi račun mogao biti obrisan, &kappname; ne može imati nikakvu referencu "
"na njega. To znači da morate obrisati sve transakcije, ili ih pomjeriti u "
"drugi račun. Ako i dalje ne možete obrisati račun, možda postoje neke "
"transakcije koje upućuju na taj račun, koje možda nisu vidljive u knjizi "
"salda. Trebate obrisati sve buduće transakcije i raspored, ili ih prebaciti "
"u drugi račun."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export Questions"
msgstr "Pitanja u vezi uvoza i izvoza"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where do I find some more information about OFX parameters?"
msgstr "Gdje mogu naći više informacija o OFX parametrima?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the web with specific questions can sometimes provide useful "
"results, but there is still one site which might give you more information: "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.ofxhome.com/\">OFX Home</ulink>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous questions"
msgstr "Razna pitanja"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why is there no translation for 'my' language?"
msgstr "Zašto nema prijevoda za 'moj' jezik?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:263
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; uses the &kde; settings for language, so first, make sure that "
#| "your region and language settings are correct. If they are, the most "
#| "likely reason is that no one has offered to translate it yet. Translating "
#| "&kde;/&Qt;-based applications is very simple, and does not require any "
#| "programming skills. If you would like to translate &kappname; into your "
#| "language, please post a message to the proper <ulink url=\"http://l10n."
#| "kde.org/teams-list.php\">team mailing list</ulink>. Should you fail to "
#| "find your language in the list or could not contact the team members "
#| "please mail directly to the <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-i18n-doc@kde.org"
#| "\">KDE translation mailing list</ulink> (<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde."
#| "org/mailman/listinfo/kde-i18n-doc\">subscription</ulink> required) and we "
#| "will give you the details on how you can easily provide a translation for "
#| "&kappname;."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; uses the &kde; settings for language, so first, make sure that "
"your region and language settings are correct. If they are, the most likely "
"reason is that no one has offered to translate it yet. Translating &kde;/"
"&Qt;-based applications is very simple, and does not require any programming "
"skills. If you would like to translate &kmymoney; into your language, please "
"post a message to the proper <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php"
"\">team mailing list</ulink>. Should you fail to find your language in the "
"list or could not contact the team members please mail directly to the "
"<ulink url=\"mailto:kde-i18n-doc@kde.org\">&kde; translation mailing list</"
"ulink> (<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-i18n-doc"
"\">subscription</ulink> required) and someone will give you the details on "
"how you can easily provide a translation for &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; koristi &kde; postavke za jezik, tako da se prvo osigurajte da su "
"postavke vašeg regiona i jezika ispravne. Ako jesu, najvjerovatniji razlog "
"za to je da se još uvijek niko nije ponudio za prijevod. Prevođenje &kde;/"
"&Qt;-baziranih aplikacija je veoma jednostavno, i ne zahtijeva nikakve "
"programerske vještine. Ako biste htjeli da prevodite &kappname; na svoj "
"jezik, molimo pošaljite poruku na pravi  <ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org/"
"teams-list.php\">tim mail lista</ulink>. Ako ne uspijete pronaći svoj jezik "
"u listi, ili ako ne možete kontaktirati članove tima, molimo pošaljite mail "
"direktno na <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-i18n-doc@kde.org\">KDE prijevod mail "
"lista</ulink> (<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-i18n-"
"doc\">subscription</ulink> required) i mi ćemo vam dati detaljne informacije "
"o tome kako možete prevesti nešto za &kappname;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why did the version number jump from 1.0.5 to 4.5, and what happened to "
"KMyMoney2?"
msgstr ""
"Zašto je broj verzije skočio sa 1.0.5 na 4.5, i šta se desilo sa KMyMoney2?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:289
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The use of KMyMoney2 was a historical legacy from when the project went "
#| "from &kde; 1 to &kde; 2. To avoid changing the name every time there was "
#| "a new &kde; version, we decided to stick with &kappname;."
msgid ""
"The use of KMyMoney2 was a historical legacy from when the project went from "
"&kde; 1 to &kde; 2. To avoid changing the name every time there was a new "
"&kde; version, we decided to stick with &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Korištenje KMyMoney2 je bilo historijsko nasljeđe kada je projekat prešao sa "
"&kde; 1 na &kde; 2. Da bi se izbjeglo mijenjanje imena svaki put kada bi "
"nastala nova &kde; verzija, odlučili smo se da ime ostane &kappname;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:294
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first version of &kappname; that was considered sufficiently stable "
#| "was labeled 1.0, even though it ran under &kde; 3. As the project is now "
#| "becoming more closely aligned with &kde; we decided to use the same major "
#| "release number."
msgid ""
"The first version of &kmymoney; that was considered sufficiently stable was "
"labeled 1.0, even though it ran under &kde; 3. As the project became more "
"closely aligned with &kde; we decided to use the same major release number."
msgstr ""
"Prva verzija &kappname; za koju se smatralo da je dovoljno stabilna je bila "
"označena sa 1.0, iako je funkcionisala pod &kde; 3. Kako projekat sada "
"postaje sve bliskiji sa &kde; odlučili smo koristiti isti broj značajnog "
"izdanja."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I report a bug? How can I request a new feature?"
msgstr ""
"Kako mogu prijaviti grešku u programu? Kako mogu zatražiti neku novu "
"funkcionalnost?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:308
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The developers encourage your feedback. See the section on <link linkend="
#| "\"firsttime.contact\">Contacting the Developers / Reporting Bugs</link>."
msgid ""
"The developers encourage your feedback. See the section on <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.contact\">Contacting the Developers/Reporting Bugs</link>."
msgstr ""
"Razvojni inženjeri vas ohrabruju za ostavljanje dojmova. Pogledajte paragraf "
"na <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">Kontaktiranje razvojnih inženjera / "
"Prijavljivanje programskih grešaka</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why isn't there an easy way to print some scheduled transactions, or part of "
"the ledger, or ..."
msgstr ""
"Zašto ne postoji jednostvan način za printanje nekih zakazanih transakcija, "
"ili dijela knjige salda, ili ..."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look in the <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">Reports</link> section. "
"Many of the reports actually provide an easy way to print thing you can't "
"quite do directly from the ledger or other screens."
msgstr ""
"Pogledajte u <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">Izvještaji</link> "
"paragrafu. Mnogi izvještaji ustvari pružaju lagan način za printanje stvari "
"koje ne možete printati direktno iz knjige salda ili nečeg drugog."

